{
  "id": "cli/lint",
  "title": "ng lint",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  \n\n\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n  <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n    {\n      \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n      \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n      \"itemListElement\": [\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli\", \"name\": \"CLI\" } },\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli/lint\", \"name\": \"lint\" } }\n      ]\n    }\n  </script>\n    <a href=\"cli\">CLI</a>\n</div>\n\n  \n<header class=\"cli-header\">\n  <h1 id=\"ng-lint\">ng lint<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/lint#ng-lint\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n</header>\n\n\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"cli-body\">\n    \n    <p translation-origin=\"off\">Runs linting tools on Angular app code in a given project folder.</p>\n\n    \n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">ng <span class=\"cli-name\">lint</span> &#x3C;<var>project</var>> [<var>options</var>]</code-example>\n\n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">ng <span class=\"cli-name\">l</span> &#x3C;<var>project</var>> [<var>options</var>]</code-example>\n\n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"arguments\">Arguments</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Argument</th>\n      <th>Description</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td><code>project</code></td>\n    <td>\n      <p translation-origin=\"off\">The name of the project to lint.</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"options\">Options</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Option</th>\n      <th>Description</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--configuration=<var>configuration</var></code>\n        <br>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">-c=<var>configuration</var></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Specify the configuration to use.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--exclude</code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Files to exclude from linting.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--files</code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Files to include in linting.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--fix=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n--<span>fix</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noFix</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Fixes linting errors (may overwrite linted files).</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--force=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n--<span>force</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noForce</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Succeeds even if there was linting errors.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--format=<var>format</var></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Output format (prose, json, stylish, verbose, pmd, msbuild, checkstyle, vso, fileslist).</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--<span>help</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noHelp</span></code>\n        \n        <br>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--help=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>|<span><a href=\"api/common/JsonPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">json</a></span>|<span>JSON</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Shows a help message for this command in the console.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--silent=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n--<span>silent</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noSilent</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Show output text.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--tsConfig=<var>tsConfig</var></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">The name of the TypeScript configuration file.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--tslintConfig=<var>tslintConfig</var></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">The name of the TSLint configuration file.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--typeCheck=<span>true</span>|<span class=\"cli-default\">false</span>\n--<span>typeCheck</span>|--<span class=\"cli-default\">noTypeCheck</span></code>\n        \n        \n        </td>\n      <td>\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">Controls the type check for linting.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n    <p translation-origin=\"off\">Takes the name of the project, as specified in the  <code>projects</code> section of the <code>angular.json</code> workspace configuration file.\nWhen a project name is not supplied, uses the configured <code>defaultProject</code> of the workspace.</p>\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - cli\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/JsonPipe\n - cli\n - cli/lint#ng-lint\n-->"
}